2002-09-25  Dan Dennedy <dan@dennedy.org>
	* avc1394_simple.c: added timeout support to avc transactions.
	* avc1394_vcr.c: added avc1394_vcr_seek_timecode(), but discovered
	  it is not supported by most devices.
